data.description:
Great southside mid-century townhome on 6220 Weber Rd .2 Bedrooms 2.5 Baths 2 car garage. Large living/dining areas! Bedrooms upstairs and 2 full baths upstairs. 1/2 bath downstairs. Laundry hookup in attached garage. Large dining and great room. Patio in the back. Entry Closet.  
New Flooring throughout, New Paint, New Doors, Updated Bathrooms,  New Light and Fans, New Window Treatments. Recently replaced Dishwasher and Stove. New Kitchen Vent.
data.whatILove: Great use of space! Great 2 story townhouse Updated in 2010 with new doors, new patio door, new counters, new tile.  Two Bedrooms upstairs and 2 full sized bath upstairs.  Well kept grounds.  Association fees cover outside maintenance, water, garbage pickup.
